From: Milk-V Vega OpenWrt port
Subject: [PATCH] net: ethernet: include xy1000 subdirectory

Pulls in drivers/net/ethernet/xy1000/ (provided via files-6.12).

--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/Makefile
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/Makefile
@@ -91,3 +91,4 @@ obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_XIRCOM) += xirco
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_SYNOPSYS) += synopsys/
 obj-$(CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_PENSANDO) += pensando/
 obj-$(CONFIG_OA_TC6) += oa_tc6.o
+obj-y += xy1000/
